intro p_and_q_or_r,

cases q_or_r with q r,
-- Case Q
left,

apply p,
apply q,
-- Case R
right,

-- Case P ∧ Q

apply p,
left,
apply q,
-- Case P ∧ R
cases p_and_r with p r,
split,
apply p,
right,
apply r,
